a^n-b^n=(a-b)\sum_{k=0}^{n-1}a^kb^{n-1-k}\;.
\rm\ j=16,\ k = 125,\,\ a,b,c,d = 121,25,1900,-4,\:
\rm\:f(x) = x^n\ 
\rm{\bf Proof}\,\ \  mod\,\ j\!:
\rm\ \ \begin{eqnarray}\color{#C00}a&\equiv&\rm \color{#0A0}b\\ \rm \color{#88f}c&\equiv&\rm \color{brown}d\end{eqnarray}
\ \ \Rightarrow\ \ 
\begin{eqnarray}&&\rm f(\color{#C00}a)-\,f(b)+f(\color{#88f}c)-f(d)\\ \equiv\, &&\rm f(\color{#0A0}b)-f(b) + f(\color{brown}d)-f(d)\,\equiv\, 0\end{eqnarray} 
