1904=119\cdot 16
121^n-25^n+1900^n-(-4)^n\equiv 9^n-9^n+(-4)^n-(-4)^n\pmod{16}\equiv 0
lcm(125,16)\mid 121^n-25^n+1900^n-(-4)^n
lcm(125,16)=125\cdot 16=2000
